        <section class='coverage'>
          <header class='cover'>
            <h2>How to claim</h2>
            <p class='plans'>
              If something goes wrong with your device and it's damaged, lost or stolen, you can make a claim by visiting our
              <a href='https://devicecover.onlineclaims.com.au/' title='Online Claims'>online claims service.</a>
            </p>
            <p class='plans'>
              <a class='btn btnmain' href='https://devicecover.onlineclaims.com.au/' title='Online Claims'>Make a claim today</a>
            </p>
            <div class='benefit'>
              <div class='splitleft'>
                <h5>Stolen or lost phone</h5>
                <ul>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Step 1</strong>
                    Call your service provider immediately to block your phone or tablet and bar your SIM card.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Step 2</strong>
                    You must notify the Police to obtain a crime reference number or police report details within 48 hours.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Step 3</strong>
                    Visit our
                    <a href='https://devicecover.onlineclaims.com.au/' title='Online Claims'>online claims service</a>
                    to begin your claim.
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class='splitright'>
                <h5>Accident and sickness claim</h5>
                <ul>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Step 1</strong>
                    Visit our
                    <a href='https://devicecover.onlineclaims.com.au/' title='Online Claims'>online claims service</a>
                    to begin your claim.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Step 2</strong>
                    Download our
                    <a href='/pds/accident-sickness-claim-form.pdf' title='accident and sickness claim form'>accident and sickness claim form</a>
                    to submit your claim.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Step 3</strong>
                    Track the progress of your claim through the
                    <a href='https://devicecover.onlineclaims.com.au/' title='Online Claims'>online claims service</a>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </header>
        </section>
      </div>
