      <div class='whatwecover'>
        <section class='coverage'>
          <header class='cover'>
            <h2>Additional information for your claims</h2>
            <p class='plans'></p>
            <div class='benefits'>
              <div class='splitleft'>
                <h5>Keep your account up-to-date</h5>
                <p>Your account needs to be up-to-date to lodge an insurance claim.</p>
                <h5>Replace and repair</h5>
                <p>If it is economically viable for us to repair your mobile device with new or refurbished parts we will attempt to do so. Where we replace your mobile device we will at our option replace it with a refurbished mobile device of similar specification if available or where such a mobile device is not available we will replace it with a new mobile device of similar specification.</p>
                <h5>Claiming for accessories</h5>
                <p>If claiming for accessories, you must provide proof of purchase. Only accessories purchased with the phone or tablet are covered.</p>
              </div>
              <div class='splitright'>
                <h5>Duty of disclosure</h5>
                <p>When making a claim you must provide all factual incident details. Remember to provide all necessary information at the time of making your claim will assist the claims team to assess your claim as quickly as possible.</p>
                <h5>Lost or stolen claims</h5>
                <p>Please allow 24-48 hours for a lost or stolen claim to be assessed, and 5 business days for damage claims to be assessed, you will be notified of the outcome of your claim by mail.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </header>
        </section>
